title: Pablo-source.github.io
text:
This is my personal website. I will publish Quarto documents about Data Analysis, statistics, predictive modelling and maps created in R and Python.
The first section I have included is called City_maps, where I explore how to build several city maps in R using OpenStreetMap (OSM) information with osmdata package.
This is a Quarto website hosted on GitHub pages
To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
